      Outside of tech, I love <a href="https://strava.app.link/qCsjlvhPyTb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">running</a>, working out, and playing basketball, tennis, cricket and pickleball. I'm a fan of the Knicks, Mumbai Indians, and the Indian Cricket Team. I also love capturing moments with my camera, <a href="https://obscurifymusic.com/profile?id=di82yeudoy32fxdlble93z00e&code=6b8a4a1d0a735a23" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">exploring music</a>, and documenting life on my <a href="/blog">blog</a>.
