        <div class="item-content">
          <ul>
            <li>• GPA: 4.35/4.00</li>
            <li>• Relevant Coursework: AP Computer Science A, AP CSP, AP Statistics, AP Physics 1, AP Physics C</li>
            <li>• Clubs & Activities: Quantum Computing Club (President and Founder), FRC Team 303 (Outreach Captain), BREngineering (President), Cricket Team (Captain and Founder), BRHS Hacks (Committee Lead)  </li>
